It contains outputs of the HCP Structural Preprocessing pipeline, which is the result of applying PreFreeSurferPipeline, FreeSurferPipeline, PostFreeSurferPipeline and MSMAllPipeline.
collection_title: HCP-D Mapping the Human Connectome During Typical Development (HCP-D)
